{"tid":1598144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為何要阻止美國自焚行為？網民：擔心大量美國難民湧入中國","createTime":"2019-09-27T09:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T10:03:13.000Z","uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b481e2c94bee5432545af0293532933a9a3bd2e9","tid":1598144,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:53:21.000Z","msg":"美國國會參眾兩院外交委員會, 通過受理《香港人權及民主法案》, 提交兩院大會審議.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n委員會同時接納另外兩項法案, 包括《保護香港法案》, 要求美國政府暫停向香港, 出口防暴和人群管制裝備, 以及要求港府回應五大訴求, 譴責香港警方武力驅散示威者的法案.<br />\n<br />\n在北京, 外交部批評法案罔顧事實, 顛倒黑白, 公然為香港激進勢力和暴力分子張目, 粗暴干涉中國內政.<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港特派員公署就表示, 絕不會坐視外部勢力肆意干預香港事務, 敦促美國會立刻停止推動涉港議案的玩火把戲, 否則必將引火燒身、玩火自焚.<br />\n<br />\n國務院港澳辦說, 美國國會的目的, 是為反中亂港勢力和少數暴徒打氣撐腰, 為香港的亂局火上加油."},{"pid":"c815b9fecf284e98d2748e803bf99084a69f34ba","tid":1598144,"uid":12994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"美國 自焚？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hTc2AnC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhTc2AnC.jpg&h=4e08c7a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mgw612C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgw612C.jpg&h=6094c20c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jeuAaVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjeuAaVY.jpg&h=c6a307b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"256e879c300d5c9341b43f98b24bad231cf77d8f","tid":1598144,"uid":187640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c815b9fecf284e98d2748e803bf99084a69f34ba","tid":1598144,"uid":12994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"美國 自焚？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hTc2AnC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhTc2AnC.jpg&h=4e08c7a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mgw612C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgw612C.jpg&h=6094c20c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"